.row
  .col-xs-8.col-xs-offset-2
    %p.landing-page-text
      %em
        SUMalyzer
      is a simple web application that helps you gathering and organizing your medical data.
      Our goal is to provide robust and transparent data for yourself, your doctors and medical research.
.row
  .col-xs-8.col-xs-offset-2
    %h3.landing-page-heading
      .emoji
        🎅🏼
      Stay anonymous.
    %p.landing-page-text
      We want to build a system that stands on the shoulders of respect for privacy, security and transparent technology. The project is open source, you can inspect the source code on
      = link_to 'GitHub.', 'https://github.com/neumanrq/SUMalyzer'
.row
  .col-xs-8.col-xs-offset-2
    %h3.landing-page-heading
      .emoji
        📈
      Analytics Tooling for your therapy.
    %p.landing-page-text
      Inspect your data, make it available for your doctors if necessary
      and get insights about long-term patterns, i.e. when adjusting
      your medication and/or behavior.
.row
  .col-xs-8.col-xs-offset-2
    %h3.landing-page-heading
      .emoji
        👩‍🏫
      Currently beta.
    %p.landing-page-text
      Please note that
      %em SUMalyzer
      is a tiny side project in a very early development phase. We're sorry
      for any inconvenience! Do not hesitate to
      = link_to "contact us", "mailto:SUMalyzer-app@posteo.de"
      for questions, thoughts, criticism, ideas or similar.

